PROJETO-DE-PESQUISA.DESCRICAO-DO-PROJETO:
In this work we explore TD identification problems. Our objective is to propose an approach to support and automate the identification of different TD types through code comment analysis by considering the developers? point of view. In order to achieve our main objective, we derive four complementary goals which are described at the following:
1.	Understanding how contextualized terms, combinations, and patterns may be categorized and combined to support the identification of different TD types through the comments analysis;
2.	Create a structure that systematically allows combining terms providing a large vocabulary to support the TD identification;
3.	Develop an automated tool in order to quickly analyze developer?s comments embedded in source codes;
4.	Evaluate and evolve the approach to identify TD through code comments analysis.
